=head1 DESCRIPTION

A summary of a configuration recorder, including the C<arn>, C<name>,
C<servicePrincipal>, and C<recordingScope>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Arn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the configuration recorder.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Name => Str

The name of the configuration recorder.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> RecordingScope => Str

Indicates whether the ConfigurationItems
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/config/latest/APIReference/API_ConfigurationItem.html)
in scope for the configuration recorder are recorded for free
(C<INTERNAL>) or if you are charged a service fee for recording
(C<PAID>).


=head2 ServicePrincipal => Str

For service-linked configuration recorders, indicates which Amazon Web
Services service the configuration recorder is linked to.



